Of course, I don't think anyone's ever refered to NYC as &quot;the City of God&quot;, but everything else is kinda creepy. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
